quran[32]{c,v,t}:
  1,1,"Mi fuЙ—Й—orii innde Allah jon yurmeende huuЙ“unde juulЙ“e e heeferЙ“e fow ka aduno, jooma yurmeende hertornde julЙ“e Й“en tun ka laakara"
  1,2,Yettoore nden ko Allah jooma tageefu On woodani
  1,3,Jooma yurmeende huЙ“tidinnde e heeriinde
  1,4,Jooma Гұalngu njoЙ“diiji
  1,5,Ko Aan tan min ndewata te ko Aan tan min mballintoo
  1,6,Feewnu min e laawol pooccingol
  1,7,Laawol ngol Й“een Й“e neemin-Й—aa Й“e ngonaa tikkanaaЙ“e te Й“e majjaani
  2,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim"
  2,2,"Ndeen deftere sikke alaa he mayre, ko nde peewal wonande hulЙ“e Й“e"
  2,3,ЖҒeen goonЙ—inooЙ“e mbirniindi eЙ“e ГұiiЙ“na juulde eЙ“e nafga e ko Min njeЙ—i Й“e
  2,4,"E Й“een goonЙ—inooЙ“e ko Min njippini dow maa e ko jippinaa ado ma, eЙ“e njananaa Гұalaande wattan"
  2,5,"ЖҒeen dey ngoni ko e peewal iwngal e Joomii Й“e, ko kamЙ“e ngoni daЙ—ooЙ“e"
  2,6,"ЖҒeen yedduЙ“e ngoonЙ—intaa foti a jeertinii Й“e wolla a jeertinaani, fof foti e mum en"
  2,7,"Alla muppi Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, wirngallo woni noppi e gite maЙ“Й“e lette mawЙ—e na woodani Й“e"
  2,8,"Na woodi heen yimЙ“e wi'ooЙ“e min ngoonЙ—inii Alla e Гұalaande wattan, tawa Й“e ngoonЙ—inaani"
  2,9,"EЙ“e koda Alla e goonЙ—inЙ“e Й“e, alaa mbo Й“e kodata sonaa ko'e maЙ“Й“e tawa Й“e nganndaa"
  2,10,Ko Гұawo woni e Й“erЙ—e Alla Й“eydani Й“e Гұawu maa lette muusЙ—e njan e mum en sabu ko Й“e pennannoo
  2,11,So Й“e mbi'aama taa bonnee e lesdi ndi Й“e mbi'a minen ko min moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e
  2,12,Ko kamЙ“e tigi ngoni bonnooЙ“e kono Й“e tinataa Й—um
  2,13,"So Й“e mbi'aama ngoonЙ—inee wano yimЙ“e Й“ee ngoonЙ—iri, Й“e mbi'a mbela minen ngoonЙ—ina wano Й—aayЙ“e Й“ee ngoonЙ—iniri, kono ko kamЙ“e tigi ngoni Й—aayЙ“e kono Й“e nganndaa"
  2,14,"So tawii Й“e kawrii e goonЙ—inЙ“e Й“e mbi'a: min ngoonЙ—inii, so Й“e njeewdii e seyЙ—anooji maЙ“Й“e Й—i Й“e mbi'a: minen ko onon min ngonndi min njalkitat tan"
  2,15,Alla jalkita Й“e O Й“eydana Й“e bewre Й“e ngona e wemmbere
  2,16,"Ko Й“een ngoni soodirЙ“e peewal majjere njeeygu maЙ“Й“e alaa tono, te Й“e peewaano"
  2,17,ЖҒe nanndi ko e kuЙ“Й“uЙ—o jayngol nde ngol yaynii Alla nawi ooyre maЙ“Й“e O acci Й“e e niЙ“e Й“e nji'ataa hay huunde
  2,18,Ko fahЙ—uЙ“e muumЙ—uЙ“e wumЙ“e Й“e nduttotaako
  2,19,Wolla wano toЙ“o iwde asamaan na woodi niЙ“e e digaali e maje Й“e cukka noppi maЙ“Й“e sabu kartaali (parГұite) ngam reentaade maayde Alla noon Ombo hiЙ“indii geЙ—e heeferЙ“e
  2,20,"Majal ngal na Й—eЙ“a yulde gite maЙ“Й“e kala nde ngal yaynii Й“e njaha heen so niЙ“Й“iЙ—ii Й“e ndaroo, so Alla welano nawa nanЙ—e e gite maЙ“Й“e sabu Alla ko kattanЙ—o kala huunde"
  2,21,Onon yimЙ“e ndewee Jooma mon tagЙ—o on tagi adiiЙ“e on mbela joo kulon Alla
  2,22,"Oon mbaЙ—anЙ—o on lesdi ndi mbertu O waЙ—i Asamaan o mahoodi tiiЙ—ndi O jippini ndiyam iwde e Asamaan O yaltini heen Й“iЙ“Й“e leЙ—Й—e woni njeЙ—u mon, taa mbaЙ—anee Alla nanndidiiЙ“e te oЙ—on nganndi goonga o"
  2,23,"So tawii oЙ—on cikkitii e Kur'aana mbo Min njippini dow jeyaaЙ—o Amen o, ngaddee simoore nanndunde hembo, nodde wallidiiЙ“e mon gaa Alla so tawii oЙ—on ngoonЙ—i e nodditaandu mon ndu"
  2,24,"So tawii on mbaЙ—aani Й—um -te on mbaawataa Й—um- kulee jayngol kuЙ“Й“irtengol yimЙ“e e kaaЖҙe, ngol heblanaa ko heeferЙ“e Й“e"
  2,25,"Weltin Й“een goonЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli moЖҙЖҙi wonde Й“eЙ“ keЙ“a aljannaaji caalli na ndonga les majji kala nde Й“e njeЙ—aa toon Й“iЙ“Й“e leЙ—Й—e Й“e mbi'a ko Й—ee min njeЙ—anoo ko adii, kono si Й“e meeЙ—ii Й—e Й“e tawa eЙ—e ceerti, eЙ“e keЙ“a toon rewЙ“e laaЙ“Й“e Й“e ГұiiЙ“ida toon. @Corrected"